trailingComments.value:
*
    * Set configuration options.
    *
    * @param {Object} options
    * @param {Object} options.logLevel Current log level, can be `debug`, `info`, `warn`, `error` or `fatal`.
    * @param {Boolean} options.stringifyArguments Whether the log arguments will be stringified and then immediately
    *   parsed again to a native JavaScript structure. It helps with making sure that deeply nested reactive options are
    *   represented by their current values, and not their getters/setters.
    * @param {Boolean} options.record Whether the log will be recorded and available via the `recording` property.
